{"tid":1120720,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【和解之後】蘋果稱有意使用高通的屏下指紋識別技術","createTime":"2019-04-23T00:29:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T11:11:29.000Z","uid":23677,"like":9,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"6b665ac112d3460053750ef8bd3b43f681cb8ac1","tid":1120720,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T00:29:20.000Z","msg":"台媒《經濟日報》報道，在蘋果與高通和解後，蘋果iPhone未來除了會採用高通的5G基帶，亦有機會採用高通獨家的超聲波屏幕指紋識別方案。<br />\n<br />\n據報，高通的超聲波屏幕指紋識別方案主要由台灣廠商業成集團代工，雙方已將在超音波指紋識別技術上合作多年，三星S10的屏幕指紋識別方案就是應用以上技術。<br />\n<br />\n分析指，以往高通在處理器、4G晶片皆取得優勢，然而，由於蘋果自行開發處理器，加上5G時代展開，若高通仍想取得蘋果的大單，相信超聲波指紋識別是具吸引力的技術。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1555899833361&amp;issue=20190422\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1555899833361%26issue%3D20190422&d=%2BBr8udGLiiUmorY0Hhmb0o6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=db5571e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1555899833361%26issue%3D20190422&h=051c1886\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1555899833361&amp;issue=20190422</a>"},{"pid":"639200b8d65aed06e1e65753a19925f85eea7324","tid":1120720,"uid":9115,"like":6,"dislike":10,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T00:35:34.000Z","msg":"垃圾指紋鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec2dd9ae2b7193d040583dcc698ee7ba6aaa35c","tid":1120720,"uid":112416,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T00:36:27.000Z","msg":"技術成熟喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e86798df5c11fa6e190fe807420984319b2694b","tid":1120720,"uid":205710,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T00:49:12.000Z","msg":"蘋果又撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71388e022131777d8d77add2444c62ed